      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WATCH HER WIN (1) was in the minors two back (17.55) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 7th. Solid record here at the distance winning seven races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Rates on top in this line up. GOLDEN SUNSET (7) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (17.49) over 300m at this track. Overdue and expected to feature again. TANGLES TIPPETT (2) was among the minors three back at this track then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 2 this time where he has two wins. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. ROCKING ROMA (3) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.",
